{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 109.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for hours without interruption we saw these motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had leaders and then all the heavy armory and artillery and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this went on for a whole day and a whole night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the-- all the people-- citizens would stay out there at the sidewalks and watch like it was a parade, but we very well know it wasn't a parade.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a-- a-- a something that's what we could--we could sense it that something terrible was going to happen, but we just didn't know what, when.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we just stood there for hours at a time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember it like it was yesterday, watching all this-- the-- the organized disciplined German Army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was frightening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was frightening to see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a week later, only one week later, they have bombed, threw incinerators into the synagogue, main synagogue, and we only lived a short while from there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was a big synagogue, the main synagogue-- there were hundreds of synagogues in our town, but there was one main synagogue which was a beautiful building that was renovated shortly before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was the pride, it was the crown of the Jewish citizenry, of the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Ironically, that big synagogue was not too far from the church, from the big church.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then there was a castle, the Zamaek, Z-A-M-A-E-K, which is a Polish name for a castle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This castle predates to the 14th century.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You have all these Polish heroes and wars and kings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That castle is still there to this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Of course, it's a ruin and of course, they've renovated and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But this castle is a historic castle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This castle was within a catcall from the synagogue and the church is not far from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
